BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Cinderella
DTSTART;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260514T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260514T210000
UID:ai1ec-149723-95457@wfhb.org
DESCRIPTION:The classic tale of Cinderella like you’ve never seen it bef
 ore. Featuring Rodgers & Hammerstein’s most beloved songs—including 
 “Ten Minutes Ago” and “Stepsister’s Lament” This production is f
 ull of heart\, humor\, and a little bit of magic.YOUR ARE INVITED to join 
 us for a timeless fairy tale. Rodgers & Hammerstein’s Cinderella brings 
 a fresh\, witty\, and romantic heart to the classic story.Follow the journ
 ey of a kind-hearted young woman who\, despite being mistreated by her soc
 ial-climbing stepfamily\, never loses her spirit or her dreams. With the h
 elp of a delightfully magical Fairy Godmother\, a pumpkin is transformed i
 nto a carriage\, and Cinderella is swept away to the Royal Ball. Beyond th
 e glass slipper and the midnight deadline\, this production focuses on the
  power of kindness and the “impossible” becoming possible through a lu
 sh\, Broadway-style score and a story that proves you don’t need magic t
 o change your world. Just a little courage.
LOCATION:Little Theatre of Bedford Indiana\, 1704 Brian Ln Way\, Bedford
URL:https://wfhb.org/event/cinderella/?instance_id=95457
X-SOURCE:WFHB Community Calendar
END:VEVENT
