 rus on the stage of Indiana University’s Musical Arts Center (MAC). This
  concert will also feature a world premiere piece by Daixuan Ai.Participat
 ing choirs include the Bloomington Chamber Singers (Caio Lopes\, director)
 \, Voces Novae (Sue Swaney\, director) and the choir of the Unitarian Univ
 ersalist Church (Sue Swaney\, director)\, as well as individuals from many
  other local choirs. The choirs are all coming together under the directio
