BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Lake Lemon Sessions: Reggae Union/ Rearview Rhonda / Spanks (Caitl
 in Spangler)
DTSTART;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260517T150000
DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260517T180000
UID:ai1ec-150090-95482@wfhb.org
DESCRIPTION:Spend your Sunday afternoons lakeside at Riddle Point Park wit
 h the Lake Lemon Shoreline Sessions\, a laid-back music series featuring e
 clectic live performances\, great food\, and refreshing drinks in one of t
 he most scenic spots on Lake Lemon.Join us from 3–6 PM for an afternoon 
 of music with Reggae Union and Rearview Rhonda\, along with an opening set
  by Spanks (Caitlin Spangler). Performances take place on a small stage at
  the end of the point with beautiful lake views. In the event of inclement
  weather\, music will move to the shelter house.Food and drink will be ava
 ilable with a beer and wine garden\, along with food from The Orbit Room a
 nd Pili’s. Children under 15 are free\, though the standard parking fee 
 applies.Leashed dogs are welcome. The park includes a playground\, swimmin
 g area\, and boat ramp. Outside food and drink are permitted\; no glasswar
 e allowed.Bring a chair\, gather your friends and family\, and enjoy a rel
 axing Sunday of music\, community\, and the lake.Event byRiddle Point Boog
 ieandOrbit Room
LOCATION:7599 North Tunnel Road\, Unionville (Riddle Point Park)
URL:https://wfhb.org/event/lake-lemon-sessions-reggae-union-rearview-rhond
 a-spanks-caitlin-spangler/?instance_id=95482
X-SOURCE:WFHB Community Calendar
END:VEVENT
