UID:ai1ec-149085-95287@wfhb.org
DESCRIPTION:Featured book:Holding Hope: One Family’s Odyssey Through Lym
 e Disease and PsychosisMarabai Rose’s gripping memoir covers her battle 
 with Lyme disease\, a battle that began with respiratory failure and paral
 ysis\, as well as her husband’s descent into psychosis just after her re
 covery. Rose tells her story with a clarity\, and emotional intelligence\,
  that allows the reader to feel as if they are by her side on this odyssey
  through illness.
