SUMMARY:Nicholas Graham Hall
DTSTART;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260523T090000
DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260523T110000
UID:ai1ec-148975-95218@wfhb.org
DESCRIPTION:Nicholas isn’t just a singer-songwriter\, he’s a storytell
 er. With a guitar in hand and a well-crafted lyric\, he can weave a vivid 
 tale or deliver a powerful message in just a few verses. Nicholas draws in
 spiration from his own life\, tackling relatable themes like self-doubt\, 
 love and loss\, the political climate\, and our humanness. His music is a 
 heartfelt exploration of the human experience.
LOCATION:Two Sticks Bakery Patio\, 415 S. Washington St\, Bloomington
URL:https://wfhb.org/event/nicholas-graham-hall-7/?instance_id=95218
X-SOURCE:WFHB Community Calendar
END:VEVENT
